## MSICStakeChange type

Represents the change between two states of an MSIC Stake.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export declare type MSICStakeChange<T> = {
    stakeMSIC: T;
    unstakeMSIC?: undefined;
} | {
    stakeMSIC?: undefined;
    unstakeMSIC: T;
    unstakeAllMSIC: boolean;
};
```
